<< Thoughts on exactly how to pre pressurize the oiling system before initial 
start up? >>

Hi Steve,
Remove sparkplugs and turn the engine over till the oil pressure light and/or 
the oil pressure gauge show oil pressure.  This can be done either in the VW 
or with a starter adapter system.  Eric&Barb
